{"tid":1564943,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[方向報] 聯合國專家發信　促港府交代6·12驅散行動","createTime":"2019-09-13T03:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T03:11:50.000Z","uid":51620,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"445bb8f11abb84a0f1bfdf9ef1776f6a95c65dd8","tid":1564943,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:09:24.000Z","msg":"香港警方今年6月12日武力驅散反修訂《逃犯條例》示威者，聯合國人權事務高級專員辦事處（OHCHR）4名專家同月28日簽發信件，要求香港政府60日內交代警方涉違反國際人權法，以過度武力驅散及任意拘捕和平示威者，否則將公開信件及港府日後的回應。<br />\n<br />\n信件指OHCHR留意到有指控稱香港警方涉用過度武力，對待在立法會外和平示威的人士。當日防暴警察驅散示威者時，部分無武裝人士頭部中橡膠子彈；警方也在沒有警告的情況下，向和平示威者施放催淚彈、胡椒噴霧及發射橡膠子彈。OHCHR亦關注有人指警方當日任意拘捕享受集會及言論自由的人士。信件指不排除部分示威者有暴力行為，但整體而言是和平。<br />\n<br />\n信件又表示，特別關注警方多次近距離使用胡椒噴霧及橡膠子彈，因為會帶來顯著的受傷風險。OHCHR要求港府就指控提供進一步資料，解釋警方使用武力的理據，在限期內收不到回覆就會公開信件及日後的回應；該信件現時已上載OHCHR網站。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190911/mobile/bkn-20190911200533611-0911_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190911%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190911200533611-0911_00822_001.html&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmEpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=7bbbe3c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190911/mobile/bkn-20190911200533611-0911_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"db621f5b8cb5c427b93f1b15a57a15c8809e9e67","tid":1564943,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:09:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"91bb38888605218ef2f4f814cd267477e2079f14","tid":1564943,"uid":25185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:10:06.000Z","msg":"【 突發】和理塞 商場篇 終於出爐!922第一彈約定你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563867\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563867</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTG :<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEgVehN8bY_NbBDM8g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAEgVehN8bY_NbBDM8g&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmEpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=9c7641d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEgVehN8bY_NbBDM8g</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Whua26P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWhua26P.jpg&h=0a307b31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g0SzLka.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg0SzLka.jpg&h=aa4ea6e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4cd31a00bd894e8809a94cdc0488b0d2a61189e","tid":1564943,"uid":12824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:10:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a2d36df27fa8745583243ee34a2f21613289e0","tid":1564943,"uid":111898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:11:50.000Z","msg":"何止612<br />\n<br />\n對un期望不大 不過好過冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}